00:02:29.580 --> 00:02:34.180
There's other systems like real time dynamic lighting, which is what we're going to be

37
00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:35.180
using.

38
00:02:35.180 --> 00:02:38.100
Now, historically, this had no global illumination system.

39
00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.840
So you only had direct light.

40
00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.900
So there was no bounce light effect in the scene or anything like that for this type

